  Mishaps involving Air Force resources may happen anytime on or in the vicinity of Ellsworth AFB.  These accidents may include but are not limited to nuclear material/components, hazardous materials, toxic liqui
ds, aircraft, space shuttle, and Air Force vehicles.  This annex defines procedures to be used by the Disaster Response Force (DRF). Operations outlined in this annex include Ellsworth AFB and off-base areas for which Ellsworth AFB is the nearest military
 installation.  Civil requests for military assistance at off-base accidents may occur at anytime.
\par 
